                    <h3>From knowing to doing: evidence use in the humanitarian sector</h3>
                    <p>This assessment framework aimed at strengthening advocacy and communications capacity was developed and validated through a pilot program with 19 grantees of the Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation, spread across 11 countries of Africa, Asia and South Asia.</p>
